Package: mzmlr
Title: Read and Validate mzML Mass Spectrometry Files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Helge Hecht
Maintainer: Helge Hecht <helge.hecht@recetox.muni.cz>
Description: Provides functionality to validate and read mzML files, a standard
    format for mass spectrometry data. Implements XML parsing without relying on
    the 'mzR' package, using native R XML handling capabilities. Supports
    validation against the official mzML XSD schema and HUPO-PSI MS Controlled
    Vocabulary.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    cli,
    xml2
Suggests:
    base64enc,
    curl,
    knitr,
    openssl,
    rmarkdown,
    roxygen2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
